SimpleWayPoint

public SimpleWayPoint(String name,
                      String descrip,
                      long time,
                      List<Double> values)
Public constructor for SimpleWayPoint's. It takes a name, description, time and a List of doubles that can be null or it can have any size.
It is supposed that values is a double[]= {long, lat, alt, speed, bearing, accuracy}
It assign elements by order. If someone isn't there, constructor assign default values.
